# Runtime dependencies — human-edited source of truth.
#
# Loose version constraints only. The fully-pinned, hash-verified install
# list lives in requirements.lock and is regenerated with `make lock`.
# Everything (venv, Docker, CI) installs from the .lock, not from here.
#
# Update flow:
#   1. edit this file
#   2. `make lock`   -> regenerates requirements.lock + requirements-dev.lock
#   3. `make sync`   -> brings your venv in line with the lock
#   4. `make audit`  -> pip-audit against the new lock
#
# Pinning rationale documented inline so future-you remembers why.

